comments: Horton-Tucker (UTA) brings his arm toward Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) side and marginal contact occurs during Gilgeous-Alexander's drive.
Horton-Tucker (UTA) makes contact with Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) arm, which affects his jump shot attempt.
Williams (OKC) brushes Kessler's (UTA) arm and marginal contact occurs as Kessler gathers the loose ball.
Dort (OKC) and Clarkson (UTA) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Kessler (UTA) establishes himself in Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Kessler (UTA) establishes himself in Dort's (OKC) path and absorbs the marginal contact.
Olynyk (UTA) clamps and holds Giddey's (OKC) arm, which affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Giddey (OKC) places his collapsing hand to Markkanen's (UTA) side and marginal contact occurs during his shot attempt at the basket.
Dort (OKC) establishes himself in Horton-Tucker's (UTA) path and marginal contact occurs as Horton-Tucker defends under the pick.
Horton-Tucker (UTA) initiates contact with Dort's (OKC) arm and affects Dort's ability to maintain control of the ball.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) takes a step laterally and makes incidental foot to foot contact with Clarkson (UTA) off ball.
Markkanen (UTA) establishes himself in Dort's (OKC) path and marginal lower body contact occurs as Dort defends over the screen.
Dort (OKC) immediately slides his hand off of Markkanen's (UTA) side and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Williams (OKC) comes across Clarkson's (UTA) left arm, which affects his ability to pass.
Olynyk (UTA) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Markkanen (UTA) moves alongside Giddey's (OKC) path and absorbs the contact during the driving shot attempt.
Giddey (OKC) swipes for the ball, causing marginal contact to occur with Kessler's (UTA) arm, which he moves through and passes.
Williams (OKC) places his forearm to Clarkson's (UTA) front and marginal contact occurs during Clarkson's drive.
Markkanen (UTA) and Williams (OKC) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.
Kessler (UTA) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Dort (OKC) is moving alongside Horton-Tucker's (UTA) path and marginal body contact occurs during Horton-Tucker's drive.
Clarkson (UTA) establishes himself in Williams's (OKC) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Clarkson (UTA) establishes himself in Giddey's (OKC) path and absorbs the contact.
Dort (OKC) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Markkanen's layup attempt.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) and Olynyk (UTA) come together underneath the basket and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the loose ball.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) jumps toward the loose ball when marginal contact occurs with Olynyk (UTA).
Williams (OKC) slides his hand off the ball and onto Kessler's (UTA) arm, affecting his layup attempt.
Dort (OKC) rests his hand on Kessler's (UTA) left shoulder during his put-back shot attempt, and the contact is marginal.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) establishes himself in Markkanen's (UTA) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Kessler (UTA) cleanly blocks Joe's (OKC) driving shot attempt before incidental contact occurs.
Williams (OKC) is moving alongside Markkanen's (UTA) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
Kessler (UTA) cleanly deflects the ball away from Williams (OKC) during rebounding.
Dort (OKC) makes contact with Markkanen's (UTA) upper body that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Markkanen (UTA) is already in Dort's (OKC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Markkanen (UTA) brings his hands towards Williams (OKC) and marginal contact occurs off ball.
Giddey (OKC) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to Utah.
Markkanen (UTA) establishes himself in Dort's (OKC) path and does not deliver contact.
Agbaji (UTA) and Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the rebound.
Markkanen (UTA) brings his hand towards Giddey (OKC) and removes his hand as he releases to pursue the long rebound.
Williams (OKC) makes contact with Kessler's (UTA) arm that affects his ability to secure the rebound.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) grasps and immediately releases Kessler's (UTA) jersey during rebounding.

After passing the ball, Dort's (OKC) hand moves forward and marginal contact occurs with Olynyk's (UTA) head/neck area.   Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Agbaji (UTA) brushes Giddey's (OKC) arm after the release of his shot attempt, and the contact is marginal.
Williams (OKC) moves laterally into Clarkson's (UTA) path and initiates body contact that affects Clarkson's SQBR during the drive.
Agbaji (UTA) is moving alongside Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.

Replay review of the foul called on Agbaji (UTA) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Agbaji moves forward into Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) body and delivers contact that affects his jump shot attempt.
Williams (OKC) briefly places his hand to Markkanen's (UTA) side and removes his hand as Markkanen moves to set the pick.
Dort (OKC) moves somewhat forward towards Markkanen (UTA) and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Markkanen (UTA) is bracing for the contact from Dort (OKC) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from the contact.

Replay review of the foul called on Dort (OKC) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Dort moves into Markkanen's (UTA) lower body and delivers contact that affects his jump shot attempt.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) and Markkanen (UTA) come together at the same spot and marginal side to side contact occurs during the drive.
Clarkson (UTA) jumps to the side of Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) and avoids making contact with Gilgeous-Alexander as he contests the jump shot attempt.
